{"tid":312263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無論8牙想唔想承認都好‼️小栗有以點都會成為51或52th既センター‼️","createTime":"2017-07-07T09:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T16:42:28.000Z","uid":16063,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9982a720e9ae133b47fd7be8706bb403542ba626","tid":312263,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"ゆいゆい由去到47th開始已正式登基本店握手一姐地位‼️<br />\n由44th美音C完開始‼️<br />\n45th總選單‼️<br />\n46th卒業單‼️<br />\n47th卒業單‼️<br />\n48th比左兩個下一章總選對決既人做雙C‼️<br />\n49th總選單‼️<br />\n50th卒業單‼️<br />\n已經有六張單係未試過比番本部純血top做センター‼️<br />\n再睇下現時本部僅餘既純血TOP‼️<br />\n奈勾 48十年以黎係重視既本部官推從來唔需要兼任‼️<br />\n真子 食文春炮次數過多 握手總選兩樣都唔掂‼️<br />\n由依 總監唔會C‼️<br />\n朱里 已比營運打壓收得檔‼️<br />\n手越 無意短期卒業‼️<br />\nゆいゆい握手一單賣得快過一單‼️<br />\n年紀夠細有潛力繼續推‼️<br />\n可愛值爆燈做ICON無問題‼️<br />\n51/52th既センター點都有一單係ゆいゆい已經係必然既事實‼️<br />\n8牙們盡早接受現實‼️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/0qj85D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F0qj85D.gif&h=987d6f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/1e2e092fd13675c8580457bc3f370890.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F1e2e092fd13675c8580457bc3f370890.png&h=baed8c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/b7844bf746475a96fdcf97a0b71bd3f9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fb7844bf746475a96fdcf97a0b71bd3f9.png&h=4d538d7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5fa7f628108d829d08e68099ee036a93928730b","tid":312263,"uid":5055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"就算係反耳都不得不承認佢已經係本家一姐"},{"pid":"c5becac1ec25c7dc4ef4febd0c89a70b50c016e5","tid":312263,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算係反耳都不得不承認佢已經係本家一姐</blockquote><br />\nAKB48 49th Single 劇場盤 第三次受付終了‼️<br />\n渡辺麻友　　24/24③ 　<br />\n柏木由紀　　24/24③ 　<br />\n岡田奈々　　23/28(4)　<br />\n向井地美音　*3/28(3)　　<br />\n小栗有以　　28/28③ ‼️<br />\n村山彩希　　26/29 <br />\nゆいゆい應該就快變到得番純簽名‼️<br />\n想換過張新twitter profile pic請珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ‼️"},{"pid":"c84ede95228950bb64fdbd46cb757985be7063c7","tid":312263,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"又燈"},{"pid":"e129f359fdeb08aeec31c5bff21061d0a748cab5","tid":312263,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又燈</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/94885/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/94885/page/1</a><br />\n禾唔燈‼️"},{"pid":"4f715a23519a1c409d8c2acd312a3b56432ae4b0","tid":312263,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"營運心態: 唔推你都賣得晒，即係已經唔使擺資源喺你度<br />\n個C位留俾其他強推之恥‼️"},{"pid":"9ba649049cd9814b441ec4105b5db16e59a23940","tid":312263,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>營運心態: 唔推你都賣得晒，即係已經唔使擺資源喺你度<br />\n個C位留俾其他強推之恥‼️</blockquote><br />\nching第一年飯數字團❓<br />\n數字團不嬲鍾意谷爆一個多過分散投資‼️"},{"pid":"118f8c496ace9a6605fd111e89d07d156e22c954","tid":312263,"uid":5055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/192823_c7ca9205222ff8c65967547a6bea6aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F192823_c7ca9205222ff8c65967547a6bea6aa5.jpg&h=1ab81daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請珍惜有耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5520b560fc036b2e492c9b5ce6896fc4f3c3e892","tid":312263,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/192823_c7ca9205222ff8c65967547a6bea6aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/